description:
17/5/2009 - Fixed some stuff.Also waiting for the sniper update (and spy too!)

21/1/2009 - Modified a bit at the "/* hides ads */" section so that the ads will be completely blocked.Also I just brought the game =)

26/9/2008 - I'm done updating the front page for 4chan.They look horrible when I see the page for the first time in few months.And also I'm done on adding another classes on the background picture.To change you just need to find this section of the CSS code here :_

html,body {
font-size:20px !important;
background-color:#e9b786 !important;
background-image:url('http://img54.imageshack.us/img54/3753/pyrobp4.png') !important;
background-position: right bottom !important;
background-repeat:no-repeat !important;
background-attachment:fixed !important;
color:#FFFFFF !important;
}

As you can see you need to change the url for the background image there.Here's the background image url for each classes

engie - http://img219.imageshack.us/img219/5871/engieno4.png
heavy - http://img162.imageshack.us/img162/7839/85921433wk5.png
medic - http://img239.imageshack.us/img239/4089/medicxg3.png
pyro - http://img229.imageshack.us/img229/4782/pyrotg2.png
demoman - http://img189.imageshack.us/img189/4839/demomanc.png

the rest I'll do it later since meh final exam is just around the corner.

Thanks to the game itself I already addicted to that damn game (and the game is not mine either! A very big thanks to my fren who always letting me playing the game on his pc lol).I'll try to make another background pic for other classes as well later on....

Cheers mate!~

css:
@namespace url(http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml);

@-moz-document 
url-prefix(http://zip.4chan.org/),
url-prefix(http://cgi.4chan.org/),
url-prefix(http://img.4chan.org/),
url-prefix(http://orz.4chan.org/)
{

/*Colors tables  bg etc*/

* {
font-family:"Mona", sans-serif !important;
font-size:14px !important;
-moz-appearance: none !important
}

.delform {
color:#FFFFFF !important;
}

.pages {
background-color:transparent !important;
}

span.plus {
color:#FFFFFF !important;
}

.hr {
color:#FFFFFF !important;
}

.omittedposts{
color:#FFFFFF !important;
}

blockquote {
color:#FFFFFF !important;
max-width:870px !important;
}

table {
color:#FFFFFF !important;
}

.logo font b span{
color:#FFFFFF !important;
font-size: 200% !important;
}

#twi_table_div{
border:none !important
}

.filetitle {
color:#FFFFFF !important;
}

.spoiler { 
background-color: #FFF !important; 
color: #FFF !important; 
}

textarea{
height:10em !important;
width:45em !important;
}

img.thumb,img[src*="/thumb/"] {
background:transparent !important;
border:solid 2px #FFFFFF !important;
-moz-border-radius:2px !important;
opacity:.99 !important;
z-index:3 !important;
}

html,body {
font-size:20px !important;
background-color:#e9b786 !important;
background-image:url('http://img229.imageshack.us/img229/4782/pyrotg2.png') !important;
background-position: right bottom !important;
background-repeat:no-repeat !important;
background-attachment:fixed !important;
color:#FFFFFF !important;
}

.replymode {
background-color:transparent !important;
color:#FFFFFF !important;
}

th {
background-color:#a11e28 !important;
opacity:.90 !important;
-moz-border-radius:10px !important;
}


tr {
color:#FFFFFF !important;
}

*[id="footer"]  {
-moz-border-radius:5px !important;opacity:.90 !important;background-color:#a11e28 !important;color:#FFFFFF !important;
border:solid 2.5px #FFFFFF !important;padding: 10px 20px 16px 20px !important
}

.unkfunc{
color:#FFFFFF !important;
}

#bod1 {
background-color:transparent !important;
}

td input, td textarea{
-moz-border-radius:10px !important;
}

[class*="postername"] {
background-color:transparent !important; 
color:#FFFFFF !important
}

[class*="postertrip"] {
color:rgb(0,160,100) !important
}

[class*="abbr"]{
color:#FFFFFF !important
}

div {
color:#000000 !important;
}

* [class="boxcontent"]{
opacity:.90 !important;background-color:#a11e28 !important;color:#FFFFFF !important;
}

* [id="ft"]{
display:none !important;
}

* [class="boxbar"]{
background-color:#a11e28 !important;
}

* [id="filter-container"]{
display:none !important;
}

* [id="options-container"]{
display:none !important;
}

* [Class="logo"]{
color:#FFFFFF !important;
}

* [id="header"]{
color:#FFFFFF !important;
}

input[type="file"] {
background-color:transparent !important;
}

span [title='']{
color:#FFFFFF !important;
}

sup{
color:#FFFFFF !important;
}

.postarea .postblock{
-moz-border-radius:15px /*2px 0 0 2px*/ !important;
border:solid 0px #FFFFFF  !important;
border-right-style: dashed !important;
border:solid 2px #FFFFFF !important;
text-align:center !important;
background-color:#a11e28 !important;
color:#FFFFFF !important;
}

.postarea:hover .postblock:hover{font-weight:bold !important;color:#FFFFFF !important;}

/* hides ads */

a[target=_top]{display:none !important;}

div.logo img{display:none !important;}

iframe{display:none !important;}

div[style*="text-align: center"]{display:none !important;}

img[style*="border:"]{display:none !important;}

div[id="ad"]{display:none !important;}

a[href="http://track.teenmodels.com/track/MjU5LjEuMS4xLjEuMC4wLjA"]{
display:none !important;
}


/* hr */

hr{display:none !important;}

form hr{display:block !important;}

hr{height:0px !important;border:none !important;background:#999 !important;}


/* rounded corners */

td.reply {-moz-border-radius:5px !important;opacity:.90 !important;background-color:#a11e28 !important;color:#FFFFFF !important;
border:solid 2.5px #FFFFFF !important;padding: 0 20px 16px 0 !important}

td.replyhl {-moz-border-radius:5px !important;opacity:.90 !important;background-color:#de6761 !important;color:#FFFFFF !important;
border:solid 2.5px #FFFFFF !important;padding: 0 20px 16px 0 !important}


/* links */

a {text-decoration:none !important;color:#FFFFFF !important;}

*[class*="poster"],*[class*="linkmail"],*[class*="replytitle"],*[class*="filetitle"],*[class*="omittedposts"],*[class*="oldpost"] { color: #FFFFFF !important; border-width: 0px !important; }

*[class*="doubledash"] { color: #FFFFFF !important; }

*[class*="unkfunc"],*[class*="quotelink"],*[class*="reflink"],*[class*="quotejs"] { color: #FFFFFF !important; }

*[target="_blank"]{ color: #FFFFFF !important; }

*[class*="abbr"] { color: #FFFFFF !important; }

a.quotejs:hover, a:hover{font-weight:bold !important;color:#FFFFFF !important;}

b {color:#FFFFFF !important;}

b.quotejs:hover, b:hover{font-weight:bold !important;color:#FFFFFF !important;}

/* removes ugly borders on page overview [0,1,2...] */

table,td{border:none !important;}

td.rules{display:none !important;}



/* logo */

img + br {display:none !important;}


/* blurry thumbnails fix */

img[md5] {

height: auto !important;

width: auto !important;

}
}

/* QUICHE */
